						h2 Bio
					//- Try to match meta description
					p
						| Lorenzo Wood is a young musician from Alameda, California USA. He sings, plays guitar, drums,
						| piano/keyboards, bass, and a bit of ukulele. He also beat-boxes, and uses a Loop Station for
						| live performances. He writes or co-writes many of his own original songs. He produces and
						| records his music (using Apple Logic) and creates live performance videos.
					p
						| Lorenzo started learning to play the drums at the age of four. At the age of seven, he
						| performed in children's musical theatre productions, and restarted performances at age
						| eleven, including key roles in #[em Annie], #[em High School Musical], and
						| #[em Into the Woods]. He has been taking music/piano lessons and, more recently, voice
						| lessons. He is entirely self-taught on guitar.
					p
						| Lorenzo lists
						| #[a(href="http://www.edsheeran.com/") Ed Sheeran],
						| #[a(href="https://www.maroon5.com") Maroon 5],
						| #[a(href="http://www.charlieputh.com") Charlie Puth],
						| #[a(href="http://www.shawnmendesofficial.com") Shawn Mendes],
						| #[a(href="http://www.jamestaylor.com") James Taylor],
						| #[a(href="http://www.johnmayer.com") John Mayer],
						| #[a(href="http://www.thebeatles.com") The Beatles],
						| #[a(href="http://www.niallhoran.com") Niall Horan], and
						| #[a(href="http://www.savemesanfrancisco.com") Train]
						| as his musical influences.
					p
						| Lorenzo enjoys working with other musicians, and has recorded a number of duets for video.
						| He is often found busking at local street festivals or busy streets, by himself or with
						| support on bass or percussion. He's expecting to have his first EP, self-produced, ready
						| later this year.

